{"tid":831711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大眼涼麵正妹神似吳亞馨 聲稱有C","createTime":"2018-09-22T07:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T23:19:17.000Z","uid":72009,"like":6,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"53a477987bbae51029ba0f4041c8b6a3126ebaa9","tid":831711,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"秋老虎發威，邊吃涼麵邊看正妹太消暑！近日臉書瘋傳高雄一間涼麵攤正妹照，白皙皮膚配上水汪汪的大眼，神似藝人吳亞馨，引起網友暴動跪求「妹妹班表」。涼妹正妹本名林芮愛，除了明星臉的高顏值，還有32C的好身材，平常兼差當模特兒，有空就在「運醬涼麵」顧攤，網路爆紅後有不少粉絲朝聖，甚至還有人凌晨3點打電話訂涼麵，讓她嗲聲抱怨：「我的黑眼圈都跑出來了！」<br />\n<br />\n涼麵正妹小檔案<br />\n姓名：林芮愛<br />\n綽號：小愛<br />\n年齡：秘密<br />\n身高：160公分<br />\n體重：47公斤<br />\n三圍：32C、23、31<br />\n經歷：模特兒、通告藝人、「運醬涼麵」老闆娘<br />\n臉書粉絲團：Xia Mi Lin<br />\n資料來源：林芮愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180922/640_d2861974083b9d21486f205d69444655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180922%2F640_d2861974083b9d21486f205d69444655.jpg&h=f96715ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180922/640_cc203231ebfda1118d53db08f5e4136f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180922%2F640_cc203231ebfda1118d53db08f5e4136f.jpg&h=50182a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180922/640_00192489dcaddeb4302d6529da11bd38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180922%2F640_00192489dcaddeb4302d6529da11bd38.jpg&h=b1809778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180922/640_4af5ed5b874168cf5d45dae8fadc4b60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180922%2F640_4af5ed5b874168cf5d45dae8fadc4b60.jpg&h=b89b25bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論港女定台妺，人人聲稱有C<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor